msgid ""
"Access pre-registered models in ``BIGDATA_PUBLIC_MODELSET`` with "
"``read_odps_model()``, then run ``embed()`` and ``generate()`` at scale "
"on DPE."
msgstr ""
"介绍如何在 MaxFrame 中访问百炼公共模型集提供的模型，并运行文本 Embedding "
"与文本生成操作示例。"

msgid "Bailian LLM calling tutorial"
msgstr "百炼大模型系列调用教程"

msgid ""
"Build reusable image feature assets with distributed preprocessing, "
"DashScope multimodal embedding, and vector persistence in MaxCompute."
msgstr ""
"通过分布式预处理、DashScope 多模态 Embedding 和 MaxCompute 向量结果持久化"
"，构建可复用的图像特征资产。"

msgid ""
"Catalog OSS images with an object table, resize in a distributed MaxFrame"
" UDF, and write to Paimon on DLF."
msgstr ""
"使用 Object Table 编目 OSS 图像，通过分布式 MaxFrame UDF 缩放图片，并写入"
" DLF 上的 Paimon。"

msgid ""
"End-to-end video processing on DPE using a custom FFmpeg image: frame "
"extraction, multimodal labeling, and embedding generation."
msgstr ""
"依托 MaxFrame 的分布式处理能力，实现视频数据的端到端批量处理，将非结构化"
"视频数据转化为可检索、可分析、可复用的数据资产。"

msgid "Examples"
msgstr "示例"

msgid ""
"Extract text from OSS PDFs with ``apply_chunk``, split it into semantic "
"chunks, generate Bailian embeddings, and write vector features to "
"MaxCompute."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``apply_chunk`` 从 OSS PDF 中抽取文本，切分为语义片段，生成百炼 "
"Embedding，并将向量特征写入 MaxCompute。"

msgid "Multimodal image feature pipeline (OSS + embedding)"
msgstr "多模态图像特征生产方案（OSS + Embedding）"

msgid "MaxFrame multimodal audio operators practice"
msgstr "MaxFrame 多模态音视频算子开发实践"

msgid "OpenLake multimodal images (Object Table + Paimon)"
msgstr "OpenLake 多模态图像（Object Table + Paimon）"

msgid "PDF text parsing and Bailian embedding"
msgstr "PDF 文本解析和百炼 Embedding"

msgid ""
"Process OSS audio directly through ``.url.download()`` and ``.audio.*`` "
"operators for decode, language detection, transcription, and VAD."
msgstr ""
"展示如何基于 MaxFrame 完成音频下载与语音识别任务，将原始音频数据高效转化"
"为可用的文本结果。"

msgid "Video pipeline: frame extraction -> labeling -> embedding"
msgstr "视频处理全流程：抽帧 → 打标 → 向量化"

